            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Aggression</td><td class="px-4 py-3">More noticeable aggression during breeding season</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Typically gentler, but can be moody</td></tr>
            <tr class="bg-cream/50"><td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Affection Levels</td><td class="px-4 py-3">Bond closely but may prefer independence</td><td class="px-4 py-3">More likely to seek cuddles and attention</td></tr>
            <tr><td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">Socialization</td><td class="px-4 py-3">May be territorial and dominant</td><td class="px-4 py-3">May be shy or reserved around strangers</td></tr>
